<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_453_r1l2"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . vns haben etwıeuıl <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd kawffleẅt fürbracht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_453_r1l3">wıe Jn ʒwıſchem hof vnd ʒwıckaw in <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> geleyt etlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_453_r1l4">weͣgen <expan>aufgeſlag<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd etwıeuıl hab <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> als eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_453_r1l5">
<del rend="strikethrough">Durchlew </del> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade auch wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> mag <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_453_r1l6">wır eẅr <expan>durchleẅchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſſ den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> eẅr gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_453_r1l7">hılff vnd <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> / Darinn cʒu <expan>beweıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / nach dem ſıe auf <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_453_r1l8"><expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> troſt vnd geleyt gefaren ſınd / Damıt ſıe ʒu <expan>Jr<ex>er</ex></expan> hab <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_453_r1l9"><expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> mugen / als wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_453_r1l10">vmb eẅr <expan>durchleẅchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>ı<ex>n</ex>feſto</expan>
