</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_453" id="225v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Marggraf <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns haben etwievil
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt fürbracht, wie in zwischem Hof
                        und Zwickaw in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> geleyt etlich weͣgen
                                <expan>aufgeslag<ex>en</ex></expan> und etwievil hab
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        als ewr <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade auch wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> mag
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                                <expan>durchlewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiss, den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ewr gnade hilff und
                                <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darinn czu
                            <expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan>, nachdem sie auf
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> trost und geleyt gefaren sind, damit
                        sie zu <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> mugen, als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. Das <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> ir
                        umb ewr <expan>durchlewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>i<ex>n</ex> festo</expan>
<expan>penthecost<ex>en</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
